data.description: Welcome to 1715 Coster Rd, Lusby, MD. This charming 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom rambler is nestled on a spacious corner lot, offering both convenience and serenity. The beautiful front porch welcomes you to unwind and enjoy the neighborhood atmosphere.  Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a large living room and dining area, perfect for entertaining family and friends. The expansive layout of this home presents huge potential for customization, allowing you to create the living space of your dreams.  As you explore further, discover two cozy fireplaces, promising warmth and ambiance during the winter months.  This property is strategically located, providing easy access to grocery stores and the vibrant Solomons Island. Indulge in the local restaurant scene or embark on boating adventures, all within close reach of your new home.  The covered back patio invites you to relax and enjoy the level backyard, providing a perfect spot for gatherings or simply enjoying the tranquility of your surroundings. For those who appreciate outdoor storage, this property boasts a huge shed and covered storage, ensuring ample space for all your belongings.   Navigating this property is a breeze with the convenience of easy ramp access and a covered carport, enhancing both mobility and protection for your vehicles. 1715 Coster Rd. offers a harmonious blend of comfort, potential, and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own – schedule a showing today and envision the endless possibilities that await!
